OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776906184
OL,3,CSenior civil servant faces Mandelson
OL,4,Cquestions from MPs amid 'Cabinet
OL,5,Cdivisions'
OL,7,FAfter Sir Olly Robbins appeared before
OL,8,Fthe Foreign Affairs Select Committee
OL,9,Fon Tuesday to give damning evidence
OL,10,Fabout the role Downing Street played
OL,11,Fin the appointment of Lord Mandelson
OL,12,Fas British ambassador to Washington,
OL,13,Fit will be the turn of Cat Little, the
OL,14,Fmost senior Cabinet Office official,
OL,15,Fto appear before the same group of MPs
OL,16,Fon Thursday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
