PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776906184
OL,3,CSenior civil servant faces Mandelson
OL,4,Cquestions from MPs amid 'Cabinet
OL,5,Cdivisions'
OL,7,FMs Little last week told the Prime
OL,8,FMinister that Lord Mandelson had been
OL,9,Fgranted high-level security clearance
OL,10,Fdespite vetting officials recommending
OL,11,Fagainst it. Ms Little had known since
OL,12,FMarch about sensitive information
OL,13,Flinked to Lord Mandelson's vetting.
OL,15,FDowning Street previously said there
OL,16,Fis "absolutely no suggestion" that Ms
OL,17,FLittle's position as Cabinet Office
OL,18,Fpermanent secretary is in question.
OL,26,@xD@DOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
