OL,3,CSenior civil servant faces Mandelson
OL,4,Cquestions from MPs amid 'Cabinet
OL,5,Cdivisions'
OL,7,FCabinet divisions have emerged over
OL,8,FSir Keir's handling of the process,
OL,9,Fincluding his decision to sack Foreign
OL,10,FOffice chief Sir Olly for failing to
OL,11,Ftell him about details of the vetting
OL,12,Fdecision, according to multiple
OL,13,Freports.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Labour backbenchers have
OL,16,Fopenly voiced doubts about Sir Keir's
OL,17,Ffuture since it emerged last week the
OL,18,FForeign Office decided to appoint Lord
OL,19,FMandelson despite the fact he failed
OL,20,Fthe vetting process.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
