PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776906184
OL,3,CSenior civil servant faces Mandelson
OL,4,Cquestions from MPs amid 'Cabinet
OL,5,Cdivisions'
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, Work and Pensions
OL,8,FSecretary Pat McFadden repeatedly
OL,9,Fdeclined to say whether he believed
OL,10,Fthe sacking of Sir Olly was fair.
OL,12,FAs pressure mounts against the Prime
OL,13,FMinister, Conservative leader Kemi
OL,14,FBadenoch is said to be pressing for
OL,15,Fhis referral to the Privileges
OL,16,FCommittee claiming he misled MPs, the
OL,17,FTimes reported.
OL,19,FThe same committee found former Prime
OL,20,FMinister Boris Johnson lied to the
OL,21,FCommons over so-called partygate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
