PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776906184
OL,3,CSenior civil servant faces Mandelson
OL,4,Cquestions from MPs amid 'Cabinet
OL,5,Cdivisions'
OL,7,FThe Tory leader has suggested Sir Keir
OL,8,Fmisled the Commons when he said "due
OL,9,Fprocess" had been followed in the
OL,10,Fappointment of Lord Mandelson as
OL,11,FBritish ambassador to the US,
OL,12,Faccording to the newspaper.
OL,14,FHe has denied misleading MPs.
OL,16,FSir Keir's former chief of staff
OL,17,FMorgan McSweeney has also been
OL,18,Fsummoned to appear before the Foreign
OL,19,FAffairs Committee next week.
OL,26,@pD@aOUqD@HO]
