OL,3,CSenior civil servant faces Mandelson
OL,4,Cquestions from MPs amid 'Cabinet
OL,5,Cdivisions'
OL,7,FThe row over Sir Olly's sacking
OL,8,Fdominated the Prime Minister's
OL,9,FQuestions clash with Kemi Badenoch.
OL,11,FHe insisted Sir Olly's evidence about
OL,12,FLord Mandelson exonerated him over
OL,13,Faccusations that he had misled MPs.
OL,15,FThe mandarin's testimony "puts to bed
OL,16,Fall the allegations levelled at me by
OL,17,Fthose opposite in relation to
OL,18,Fdishonesty", the Prime Minister said.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUzD@KO]
