OL,3,CSenior civil servant faces Mandelson
OL,4,Cquestions from MPs amid 'Cabinet
OL,5,Cdivisions'
OL,7,FSir Keir's fate could be decided if
OL,8,FLabour MPs move against him after
OL,9,FMay's elections for English councils
OL,10,Fand the Scottish and Welsh parliaments.
OL,12,FYouGov projections indicated Labour
OL,13,Fwas on course for disastrous results
OL,14,Fin its former London and Welsh
OL,15,Fstrongholds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
